casebody.head_matter:
Gregg McNAMARA, petitioner,
v.
CALIFORNIA.
No. 17-9324.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 1, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
